imdb.plot outline: Extreme Series: Kaya Mo Ba 'To? Adventure Travel show (English: Extreme Series: Can You Do This?) is a Philippine reality television show that aired on TV5 since February 2, 2015, hosted by Derek Ramsay. It airs every Monday to Friday nights at 10:15PM (PST).[1]
